# Architecture Overview

## Design Approach

This project follows a modular architecture where each part of the system
has a clearly defined responsibility.

## Core Principles

- Low coupling
- High cohesion
- Scalability
- Maintainability

## Frontend Strategy

The UI is divided into:

- Components → reusable elements
- Layouts → structural patterns
- Pages → complete views

## Future Evolution

This architecture can transition into component-based frameworks
like React or Vue without major restructuring.